summary: This document is a disclosure from Fifth Third Mortgage regarding the right to receive a copy of appraisals related to mortgage loans. It outlines the process for obtaining appraisals and the associated costs, emphasizing that appraisals will be provided regardless of whether the loan closes.
keyFacts: The document outlines the right to receive a copy of appraisals for mortgage loans.
It states that an appraisal may be ordered to determine the property's value.
Borrowers can pay for an additional appraisal for their own use.
Loans are subject to credit review and approval.
Fifth Third Mortgage is identified as an Illinois Residential Mortgage Licensee.
